<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='8165:8168'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='8168:8171'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='8171:8183'>　辨定祭禮通俗譜卷一</span><br/>
